{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The first time I saw a dead person was my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- he had a heart attack when the first bomb came on Lublin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it came on Lublin, if I'm not mistaken, I was told.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was there to visit my brother in-- in the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he also had family there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His own immediate family lived in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think the first bomb, he had a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when he came home, he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember his body laying out to rest on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, in those days, things were different when people died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is the first time I saw a dead person, when my grandfather was laid out in his own house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When I was-- when the second selection came-- well, the first and the second time I saw them is when they were dancing on their robes in that square.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "By that time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a daily occurrence after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a-- a daily occurrence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were always-- there was always death somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I don't know, I seemed to overlook everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I-- I must have placed myself in a completely different place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was, most of the time, very jolly as a child when I was around my parents, and I used to sing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I think maybe that's what helped me survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I used to absorb songs, and I used to be so keen, and I wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was very seldom anything that passed by me that I didn't absorb, especially if it had to do with singing or-- or songs or verses.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
